FuncDef: This command identifies a test and create/modify the context to provide the test parameters for the named test. Subsequent to the creation of the test instance the test can be started in the OAM context.

ParaDef.Info: Identifies the SAA test name to be created or edited.
Specifies the owner of an SAA operation. If a value is not specified, the default owner will be used. 32 characters maximum. ParamDefault: Default- "TiMOS CLI"
